any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Automotive Technician requirements Must be at least 18 years old High School diploma or GED equivalent Ability to walk and stand for long periods of time Effective verbal and written communication skills Knowledge of car mechanics Ability to lift at least 50 pounds Automotive Technician related job titles: Mechanic Car Mechanic Auto Mechanic Car Technician Auto Technician Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
